    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove inheritance tax on all estates and their property worth under \u00a31 million",
        "additional_details": "With current inflation and property prices I feel it's only right that the threshold for paying inheritance tax should change from \u00a3325,000 to \u00a31 million. So, there should be no inheritance tax on estates and their property under \u00a31 million.",
        "background": "Change the inheritance tax threshold from all estates from \u00a3325,000 to \u00a31 million, so that no inheritance tax is levied on estates and the property within them up to a value of \u00a31 million.",
